iewpoints are <a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/qMDFnxivGRBKvrZG8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Mirador El Cuzco<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/Nv1iC2R2ZVUTFvZeA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Mirador Laberinto<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/tatacoa-hotels-all\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here are all your hotel options in Tatacoa.<\/a><\/p>\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29123013\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-13.jpg\" alt=\"tatacoa desert trail colombia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"tatacoa desert trail colombia\" class=\"wp-image-84572 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29123013\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-13.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29123013\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-13-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29123013\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-13-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29123013\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-13-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29123013\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-13-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\