errer noopener\">starting here<\/a>) where you will see many cactus plants (with fruits!), colorful birds, scorpions, curious goats, and sometimes even snakes. After all, &#x2018;Tatacoa&#x2019; is Spanish for &#x2018;rattlesnake&#x2019;. The trail takes about 1.5 hours to complete and is mostly flat.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Bring a lot of drinking water and some snacks because there&#x2019;s almost no option to buy this in Tatacoa Desert.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29133250\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-15.jpg\" alt=\"tatacoa desert colombia drone\"><\/noscript><img width=\"225\" height=\"338\" alt=\"tatacoa desert colombia drone\" class=\"wp-image-84582 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1279px) 100vw, 1279px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29133250\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-15.jpg 1279w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29133250\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-15-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29133250\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-15-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29133250\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-15-225x338.jpg 225w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022