c=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29113728\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-11.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-2-grey-desert\">2. Grey Desert<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Grey Desert of Tatacoa is about a 30-minute drive from the Red Desert. The landscape in this part of the desert feels even more surreal; it is nicknamed &#x2018;The Valley of Ghosts&#x2019; because of its unique shapes. You can also follow a short trail with amazing, moon-like scenery. To us, this place felt like stunning <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/turkey\/cappadocia-turkey\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Cappadocia<\/a> in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/turkey\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Turkey<\/a>. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120144\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-1.jpg\" alt=\"tatacoa desert grey\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"tatacoa desert grey\" class=\"wp-image-84553 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120144\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-1.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120144\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-1-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120144\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-1-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120144\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-1-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120144\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-1-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120144\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-1-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120144\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-1-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120144\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-1-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120144\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-1-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120144\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-1-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120144\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-1-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120144\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-1-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120144\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-1-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120144\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-1-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120144\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-1-20x30.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120144\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-1.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Both the grey and red desert of Tatacoa are a must-visit. We recommend visiting the Grey Desert at sunset as the colors are absolutely spectacular at this time.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/tatacoa-hotels-all\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here are all your hotel options in Tatacoa.<\/a><\/p>\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120210\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-7.jpg\" alt=\"tatacoa desert tour colombia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"tatacoa desert tour colombia\" class=\"wp-image-84558 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120210\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-7.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120210\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-7-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120210\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-7-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120210\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-7-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120210\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-7-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29120210\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-7-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp