inourhair.com\/colombia\/tayrona-national-park\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Tayrona National Park in Colombia<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29140720\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-22.jpg\" alt=\"Xil&#xF3;palos Trail colombia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Xil&#xF3;palos Trail colombia\" class=\"wp-image-84602 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29140720\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-22.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29140720\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-22-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29140720\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-22-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29140720\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-22-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29140720\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-22-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29140720\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-22-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29140720\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-22-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29140720\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-22-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29140720\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-22-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29140720\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-22-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022