tels as well as fancy glamping experiences. We&#x2019;ve also seen travelers wild camp in a tent in the desert, but we can&#x2019;t provide any information about this.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/mana-star-hotel\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Mana Star Hotel\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/31143854\/270600583-450x338.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Mana Star Hotel<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                \n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/penon-tatacoa\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"El Pe&#xF1;on De Constantino\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/31143846\/228537615-450x338.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">El Pe&#xF1;on De Constantino<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-villavieja\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotels-all-villavieja\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Villavieja<\/a><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Villavieja has more accommodation options. These are generally cheaper, and some have a small pool for you to cool down (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/tatacoa-star-eco-hotel\/\">we stayed at Star Eco Hotel<\/a>). It is a sleepy but lovely town with a few restaurants and supermarkets where you can get water for an affordable price. The only downside is that it is about 10 minutes driving with a tuk-tuk or a 1h+ walk to the Red Desert.&#xA0;(<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotels-all-villavieja\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Click here to see all accommodations in Villavieja<\/a>)<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/tatacoa-star-eco-hotel\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Star Eco Hotel\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/31142920\/283460034-450x338.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Star Eco Hotel<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                \n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/villa-paraiso\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Hotel Paraiso\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/31143440\/81957212-450x338.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Hotel Paraiso<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29144925\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-27.jpg\" alt=\"Villavieja visit tatacoa desert colombia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Villavieja visit tatacoa desert colombia\" class=\"wp-image-84618 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29144925\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-27.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29144925\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-27-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29144925\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-27-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29144925\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-27-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29144925\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-27-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\