rer noopener\">book a biking tour online<\/a>. <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>By tuk-tuk<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Guided tuk-tuk trips can be booked from the main square in Villavieja, where drivers will be waiting. We booked our trip with Joe; he&#x2019;s a fantastic English-speaking guide, and you can WhatsApp him to make a reservation in advance (recommended). Expect to pay about 85 &#x2013; 110 USD for a two-day tuk-tuk guided tour, which can be split among three people.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tour \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tour\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/api.whatsapp.com\/send?phone=573104030102&amp;text=Hi%20Joe%2C%20I%20found%20your%20number%20via%20the%20Salt%20in%20our%20Hair%20travel%20website.%20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Click here to open Whatsapp and send Joe a message<\/a> or call +57 310 403 0102.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29105357\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-10.jpg\" alt=\"tatacoa desert guided tuk tuk\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"tatacoa desert guided tuk tuk\" class=\"wp-image-84544 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29105357\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-10.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29105357\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-10-480x6